code: import axios from'axios';const API_URL="http://localhost:5001/api";export const createMusician=async musicianData=>{const response=await axios.post(API_URL,musicianData);return response.data;};export const updateMusician=async(id,musicianData)=>{const response=await axios.put("".concat(API_URL,"/").concat(id),musicianData);return response.data;};export const getAllMusicians=async()=>{const response=await axios.get(API_URL);return response.data;};export const getMusicianById=async id=>{const response=await axios.get("".concat(API_URL,"/").concat(id));return response.data;};export const searchMusicians=async query=>{const response=await axios.get("".concat(API_URL,"/search?name=").concat(query));return response.data;};
